Got it, I'll remove the "Note" and make sure all of them are capitalized.
Unfortunately adding an extra space doesn't do anything since Markdown/HTML combine one or more spaces and render them as only one. But I can always add the ugly   to give them an extra space, it does help on the visualization so I'll add them.
